RXPGuides.RegisterGuide([[
#retail
#version 20
#group RestedXP Midnight
#subgroup Pre-Turnins
#name a) Pre-Turnins Booklet
#internal
step
+Stormwind Quests can be turned in at the start: under "Guide: Prepturnins" or "Miscellaneous Turnins"
*Expect heavy crowding in the Midnight intro at launch. Turning in some Pre-Quests before may reduce lag/DCs.
*In Retail, being far enough behind the pack is often manageable or even advantageous.
step
+Global Quests can be turned in from everywhere(some pet battles for example) ideally those are turned in an area with an XP Buff
*The guide will guide you to Ohn'ahran Plains for 5% extra XP when it's time to turn them in.
*If you want to do them at the start select "First Crafts & Global Turnins" keep in mind you will need to return to this guide if you want to do first crafts later.
step
+Should you ever be stuck in any prep guide and you do not want to waste any time manually skips the steps or select the chapter after turnins.
step
+We only cover Kun'lai Turnins, netherstorm is not supported
]])
