RXPGuides.RegisterGuide([[
#retail
#version 1
#group RestedXP Midnight
#name a) Quest Booklet
#internal
step
+Please read this section carefully.
*It explains how to use the guide and avoid common mistakes.
step
+This guide is designed to maximize experience and efficiency at launch.
*It is divided into three main sections:
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Prepping Quests|r
+Prepare quests in advance and hold them completed for launch day turnins
*This allows for fast experience as soon as leveling is unlocked.
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Prepping Items|r
+Collect items that increase leveling speed and quality of life.
*These items reduce downtime and improve overall efficiency
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Turnin Route|r
+Follow a structured route to turn in all prepared quests
*This section is integrated into the overall leveling route |cRXP_WARN_(normal & multibox)|r.
*Expect to turn in prepared quests not only at level 80, but throughout levels 80–90.
*Most prepared quests scale with your level.
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Accidental Turnins|r
+Any addon that auto-accepts or auto-turns-in quests |cRXP_WARN_(aside from RestedXP)|r can cause accidental turn-ins.
+This may result in lost experience before launch, use other addons at your own risk.
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Accountwide Quests|r
+Many quests in this guide can only be completed once per account or character
+If the guide skips many steps, this is by design
+It usually means those quests were already completed and unfortunately cannot be used for launch-day turn-ins.
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Time & Choice|r
+Each quest section clearly states its purpose and estimated time investment.
+This allows you to decide whether you want to pursue it.
step
#title |cFFFCDC00Estimated Total XP|r
+Estimated XP if you have access to every quest (none unavailable) as Horde: about 696,000 XP without buffs, reaching roughly 85% of level 81.
*Alliance: roughly 70% of level 81.
]])
