RXPGuides.RegisterGuide([[
#retail
#group RestedXP Midnight
#name |cRXP_WARN_Before You Pick a Guide|r
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Default:|r This guide will do the campaign, delves and some side quests (identical to Campaign & Sidequests). It will skip side quests if you're overleveled. This is the fastest route if you don't want to use Warmode and are not crafting at the end.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Campaign & Sidequests:|r This guide will do the campaign, delves and some side quests. It will skip side quests if you're overleveled. This is the fastest route if you don't want to use Warmode and are not crafting at the end.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Campaign & Delves:|r This guide will do the campaign and all delves. It has no built in xp skips and expects you to craft at the end.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Adventure Mode:|r This guide is for your alts after you have done the campaign once. You can do the chapters in any order and stop early if you want to craft for the last level.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_(80-90) Campaign:|r If you only want to do the campaign then select the first chapter of the Eversong Woods campaign.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Delve Worldtour:|r This guide does all delves and their quests. If you want to turn in all the quests in the end then skip the turn in steps at the beginning.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Delves:|r Allows you to individually pick each delve.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Sojourner:|r This guide lets you select individual zone storylines required for the Sojourner achievement, which is needed for Midnight Pathfinder to unlock steady flight.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_Miscellaeneous:|r Additional Storylines for achievements.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_(90) Campaigns:|r The level 90 Campaign when you reach max level.
step
+|cRXP_PICK_(90) Storylines:|r Level 90 Storylines
step
+If you want to use the multibox functionality, select any 80–90 route. Then open RestedXP Options under Guide Routing enable “Multibox Mode”.
]])
